&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate thrives in fast-moving environments, is flexible in ambiguity, is an excellent writer, and can synthesize complex information (such as technical specs or policy details) into clear and compelling messaging. They excel at working cross-functionally to develop resonant stories that drive adoption of Claude and bolster Anthropic’s corporate reputation.&lt;/p&gt;
